# Ensure shell scripts always check out with LF line endings, regardless of
# the cloning machine's core.autocrlf setting. A CRLF shebang line breaks
# `exec ./docker-entrypoint.sh` inside the Linux container (Windows clones
# with autocrlf=true — git's own recommended default — would otherwise
# silently corrupt these on checkout, crash-looping the api container).
*.sh text eol=lf
